1. All libraries prefixed with 'BL' in their name include data from iPTMnet and PhosphositePlus.

iPTMnet database is protected under the CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 (Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International) license .
This means that you are free to copy and redistribute the material in any medium or format as long as you comply with the following terms:
